          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-12-1691497646541-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has caramelised, add <strong>half</strong> the<strong> miso paste</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and stir it all together</p><p>Transfer the <strong>onion</strong> to a bowl (reserve the pan!) – this is your <strong>miso onion</strong></p><p>Wipe the reserved pan clean and return it to a medium-high heat with a little drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> patties </strong>and cook for 6-7 min on each side or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – these are your<strong> umami patties</strong></p>",
